\p{\strong{After reading the workflow, follow it exactly.}}

\p{</routing>}

\p{<verification_loop>}

\p{After every interpretation, verify:}

\ol{
\li{\strong{Did you use relative positions?} Never stated "A is 8" without context}
\li{\strong{Did you reference the arrow?} All trait interpretations relative to arrow}
\li{\strong{Did you compare Survey vs Job?} Identified any behavior modification}
\li{\strong{Did you avoid value judgments?} No traits called "good" or "bad"}
\li{\strong{Did you check EU?} Energy utilization calculated if both graphs present}
}

\p{Report to user:}

\ul{
\li{"Interpretation complete"}
\li{Key findings (2-3 bullet points)}
\li{Recommended actions}
}

\p{</verification_loop>}

